# Maintainer playbook (local only)

**Canonical template:** [snippets/maintainer-local/MAINTAINER.md.example](snippets/maintainer-local/MAINTAINER.md.example)

```bash
./snippets/bootstrap-maintainer-local.sh
```

That copies the template to gitignored **`MAINTAINER.md`** in the bundle root. Do not commit org names, internal repo slugs, or machine-specific paths.

See also [snippets/maintainer-local/README.md](snippets/maintainer-local/README.md).
